{"tid":420230,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦藍牙連接唔到xbox one手制","createTime":"2017-10-01T08:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T14:22:12.000Z","uid":21369,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c7575885e7a6ca94bad9da9bde1198da1207e03","tid":420230,"uid":21369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:28:21.000Z","msg":"頭先買左隻藍牙手指(ApaxQ BTDG-403)<br />\n諗住用黎連落個xbox one手制<br />\n裝完個driver之後都search到個手制<br />\nclick完佢就寫&quot;請稍後...正在配對...&quot;<br />\n等好耐之後都係唔得, 試咗好多次都係張圖咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/01/162609_02e428d287ebdff811ad45e61baaf943.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F01%2F162609_02e428d287ebdff811ad45e61baaf943.png&h=913bc9df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我用另外個藍牙喇叭咁樣做就好快連接咗<br />\n本身個手制用USB線都連接到<br />\n<br />\n有無咩方法可以解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d3a14758e733a552b1b2b1af8328ea4b6db749","tid":420230,"uid":21369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:43:49.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7b66cd4f0c47dfdf52f5675583e4fa8122e7be","tid":420230,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:33:29.000Z","msg":"呢d唔係要press 個pairing 掣既咩"},{"pid":"6e5008b8cd18c4a8ff32cda8bd7d7a86cb6b6a49","tid":420230,"uid":21369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d唔係要press 個pairing 掣既咩</blockquote><br />\n要keep 住噤實?<br />\n我見佢話噤三秒等佢閃得勁快就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf20ea994cc6e55714b646703ae806f118b112c","tid":420230,"uid":128613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢d唔係要press 個pairing 掣既咩</blockquote><br />\n要keep 住噤實?<br />\n我見佢話噤三秒等佢閃得勁快就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"h